{"tid":234064,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《異空戰士》導演：續集片名已定，湯姆克魯斯與愛蜜莉布朗興致高昂","createTime":"2017-05-08T03:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T07:10:48.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c026b86dacedee73f874140402485c50b6efbebd","tid":234064,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D612&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4fe05dd1\" target=\"_blank\">http://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=612</a><br />\n<br />\n喜歡《明日邊界》的朋友們歡呼吧！因為根據該片導演 Doug Liman跟媒體訪問時說到，《明日邊界》續集絕對會發生，只是擋期問題而已。<br />\n<br />\n根據導演說法，續集的片名目前已定為：Live Die Repeat and Repeat，甚至腳本初版都已經完成。雖然時程未定，但是看來劇組的成員們都躍躍欲試！<br />\n<br />\n導演：＂我們有個很棒的（續集）故事，遠比第一集好很多，而我已經很愛第一集了！片名是 Live Die Repeat and Repeat，湯姆跟愛蜜莉都很興奮！續集一定會發生的，只是時間與檔期問題而已！＂<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：ScreenRant"},{"pid":"cc7f710b6d3eabd02ab06d8c5befcb31bad28705","tid":234064,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:07:54.000Z","msg":"乜撚野柒名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac5ce0380e398f4d8c0cc5e425f693ee906bda6","tid":234064,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野柒名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一集tagline係Live Die Repeat<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae9bbcb4790fe6f23eb94cab07151c819204ada","tid":234064,"uid":103490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D612&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ